reviews.text: We arrived, not realizing the kitchen was closing, and they were so nice and let us place our order.  The food was really good.  The service was the right amount of checking in on us, and it was the perfect night to sit outside and enjoy a meal.

We enjoyed the calamari and artichoke dip as appetizers. They had raspberry sangria as the special.  Yum! As main course I had the steak tacos and Truffle fries which were excellent!! Our waitress was excellent. Very good vibes. We went early but I could see this restaurant/bar being really fun at night to have a drink and socialize.  Really cute outdoor space to sit too.

Harp & Fiddle family owned restaurant

I recently dined at Harp & Fiddle which is family owned and had an exceptional experience. The ambiance was warm and inviting, making it perfect for both casual outings and special occasions. The food was outstanding, with every dish bursting with flavor and beautifully presented. The drinks menu was equally impressive, offering a wide selection of creative cocktails and a well-curated wine list. The staff was attentive and knowledgeable, adding to the overall enjoyment of the evening. Highly recommend this place for anyone looking for great food and drinks!

I had my daughters baby shower at Harp and Fiddle last weekend.  From the start, it was a great experience.  Monika, the coordinator was extremely responsive and helpful.  The staff was spot on and their service was outstanding, as was the food.  We had our event in the front section and it felt private, but, also was so bright and open feeling .  I would highly recommend Harp and Fiddle for any private event.  Thank you for making the shower such a great day!  I will definitely be back for our next party!

We went there for my sisters birthday, Eileen was our server, she was the best! Cheese curds were delicious and Margarita flat bread was super good! Eileen went above and beyond! She did such a great job and was just the sweetest! We would definitely go back.

editorial_summary.overview: Rustic-contemporary tavern with American & Irish comfort food, craft beer, a patio & live music.
